data.description: Move in ready! You know the saying ''location, location, location?'', well this is it! This lovely three bedroom, two bath stunner is perched atop a large manicured lot located just off the parkway and within 5 minutes of I-40. It is very close to the many Sevierville attractions and the Gateway to the Smokies. The picturesque mountain views will greet you every time you pull into the neighborhood and take your breath away. This home boasts an open eat-in kitchen, large bedrooms, and an unfinished basement perfect for storage or finishing out. This home is part of an estate and is being sold ''as is''. Don't let this gem get away, schedule a private showing today!
